  "texts": [
    "Developing countries face financial constraints, and the high cost of implement ing and maintaining advanced technologies may limit widespread adoption.",
    "Moreover, while pilot projects in countries such as India and Brazil have shown promising results, their long-term sustainability is uncertain, particularly in regions where government funding fluctuates [31].",
    "Addressing this challenge requires greater emphasis on public-private partnerships and international collaboration to ensure ongoing support for digitization initiatives.",
    "• Ethical and Data Privacy Considerations.",
    "Another aspect that requires further elaboration is the ethical framework surrounding data privacy and cybersecurity in digitized legal systems."
